Title: Murloc Mania
Description:
The shore is littered with shipwrecks. This must be where the lost expedition crashed.

We cannot begin our search until our soldiers are healed. There is no honor in leaving the fallen behind!

Our medical supplies were stolen by murlocs. Slay the pests and recover our first aid kits.
ObjectivesText: Recover 6 First Aid Kits from Murlocs.
PortraitGiverText: Murlocs have stolen crucial first aid supplies!
RewardText: Excellent work. Let's get the survivors back on their feet.

Objectives.Text: First Aid Kits recovered from defeated Murlocs
